messages.content: Dear Resident, On Thursday you not only have the opportunity to vote for who represents you in Longbridge Ward as your Councilor, but also who will be the next Member of Parliament for our constituency, Birmingham Northfield. Your two votes this May 7th couldn't be more important. As things stand the outcome, both locally and nationally, is too close to call and your vote could make the difference.

issues.governance: We will continue to hold the Council to account and to work to make our area clean, even when the Council won’t. We are still fighting Labour's unfair Garden Tax. We will continue to work to make our roads safer and pothole free.

contactInformation.address: Birmingham Northfield Conservatives, 1-7 Langley Road, Birmingham, B29 6HR
